summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition of certain property in Blocks 452 and 453, Seattle Tide Lands; Block 17, First Plat of West Seattle by the West Seattle Land and Improvement Company; Blocks 164 and 167, Seattle Tide lands; Block 50, Yesler's Third Addition; Block 14, Lake Union Addition; Block 3, Calligan and Coryell's Addition; Blocks 9 and 10, Law's 2nd Addition; Block 124 A.A. Denny's Broadway Addition; Block 13, Burke's Second Addition Blocks 445, 445A, 448 and 448A, Seattle Tide Lands and Seattle Tide Lands Extension No. 1; block 19, Walla Walla Addition; and Blocks 64 to 77, 80 to 90 and 92 to 98 inclusive, Seattle Tide Lands, as permanent open space for recreational and scenic purposes; making a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund and declaring the emergency therefor.
